Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.25,0:00:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向往天空 亲近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.64,0:00:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翱翔于天空的神秘力量开始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.35,0:00:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.75,0:00:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.05,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天之边际云之彼方存在着一片黄金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.22,0:00:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个故事讲述了一个追寻梦想自由生存的天空盗贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.01,0:00:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空盗团少年——酷的波澜起伏的爱和冒险的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.80,0:02:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与守护翼敌对并想夺走七煌宝树蕾的ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.90,0:02:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那却是存在\N于煌珠的乌托邦——煌珠乐园里面的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.13,0:02:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在为了让蕾成为新的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.46,0:02:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们动真格地要夺走酷的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.75,0:02:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟酷等人是否能挡住这一攻势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.61,0:02:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说煌珠乐园和ChaosChoir是同一体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出神圣之矢{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射中之人绝非等闲{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾主所统之福地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.51,0:02:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箭中标的{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死于此箭之下{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.02,0:03:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二十二唱 被埋葬的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你碰酷一根手指的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.56,0:03:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再偏下发射一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打中希丝卡他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.54,0:03:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比预想的提早出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 好兴奋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.60,0:03:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是休纳贝尔的侦察艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基卢特鲁 阿京娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时先撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须回煌珠乐园整军备战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现世之人{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我为虫{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎吱嘎吱{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.87,0:04:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薄薄一片{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集于我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化作心叶{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.38,0:04:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芸芸众生{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗野之魂{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涤除殆尽{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须臣服{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首领之人{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚猛之力{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈加横溢{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.60,0:04:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩断一切{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去确认受损情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.37,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你们迟早要做个了结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.54,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 请交出蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.77,0:05:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.31,0:05:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.10,0:05:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.08,0:05:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊 老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷的情况怎么样 龙威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.62,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身受到猛烈攻击 昏过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为最好让医生好好检查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.99,0:06:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能求助于休纳贝尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向休纳贝尔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.02,0:06:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.73,0:06:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 向休纳贝尔寻求救助可能有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是医治酷他们是最紧急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾和酷的身体就用我们的双手来保护吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.25,0:06:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.47,0:06:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛 你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.10,0:06:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊芙 我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护翼的进攻似乎也比预期提前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 欧珐斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊芙大人已经没有力量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.53,0:07:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠现存的拟煌珠对抗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.70,0:07:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把在煌珠乐园里的所有煌珠集合到广场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.30,0:07:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和守护翼作战之前我有话要传达给她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.22,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊芙大人 请再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受损的操纵器修好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还需再花一点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就先把系统修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.74,0:08:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请出示证件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.72,0:08:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是法鲁克总监麾下的煌珠保护官希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事关最高机密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求立即会见指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.53,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是希丝卡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来看望我了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇雅姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.57,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙威鲁德前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况我已大致了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.17,0:09:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔罗 带酷德他们去一趟医务室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.19,0:09:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 你不去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.81,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有重要的事要和沙威鲁德前辈说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算赶上了 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.79,0:09:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法鲁克总监和克鲁斯辅佐官都很担心希丝卡你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总监和辅佐官他们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.37,0:09:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以前辈救了我们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.68,0:10:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么休纳贝尔的侦察艇会在煌珠乐园的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.98,0:10:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上早就对守护翼示以敌意的ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.73,0:10:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是煌珠乐园的另一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.21,0:10:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.40,0:10:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是听几个貌似ChaosChoir的干部的人那么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.58,0:10:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话你也应该能理解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.22,0:10:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护翼的议会已经决定消灭反叛人类的煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.33,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久就应该会向守护翼全军下达进攻煌珠乐园的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ChaosChoir的所作所为的确无法原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.64,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.58,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此就以歼灭为目的\N而进攻不是违反了守护翼的理念了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希丝卡也是这么想的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.81,0:11:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也认为必须阻止这次进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.41,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为煌珠和人类不应该互相仇恨战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.84,0:11:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.29,0:11:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么才能阻止守护翼和煌珠乐园的战斗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.01,0:12:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 有件东西想给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.65,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和七煌宝树一起旅行的你可能会想到些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边不是有个旧包吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打开看看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.78,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久守护翼就会对这个煌珠乐园发动攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.14,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 让我们来埋葬古老的传说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.89,0:12:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古老的石板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.19,0:13:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说曾在煌珠乐园内的巨大石板碎裂后被丢弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是它的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻在上面的是文字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.95,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.78,0:13:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很久以前的文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记载着古老传说中的一节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煌珠乐园想要抛弃的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈能看懂这文字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能看懂一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.04,0:13:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前人并非尽是争战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共同唱颂内心颂词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缔造奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.27,0:13:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据曾在煌珠乐园流传下来的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.66,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在古老年代 煌珠和人类一同唱颂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造了各种各样的奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.00,0:13:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是人类只追求战斗的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.86,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢弃了很多颂词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.29,0:14:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔑视我们煌珠为道具 只是用来战斗的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是愚蠢的错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煌珠不是人类的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.96,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应说是煌珠为了发挥伟大的力量而利用人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.82,0:14:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而自大的人类却想要进攻这煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.68,0:14:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁我们的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.70,0:14:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护者们既然想战斗 那我们也不应示弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.24,0:14:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此以我们的力量保卫煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击退守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将该是煌珠统治世界这个道理告知守护者与人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古老的传说已经不需要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.21,0:14:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该是创造新的传说的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.09,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.54,0:15:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈是觉得若能唤醒\N煌珠和我们守护者曾经拥有的创造奇迹的力量的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.61,0:15:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能成为制止战斗的关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.03,0:15:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是怎样才能唤醒那种力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一关键部分不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤醒颂词的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前人并非尽是争战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共同唱颂内心颂词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缔造奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共同...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.28,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.98,0:15:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人一定能唤醒曾经失去的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.94,0:15:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你一定知道些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.08,0:15:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起相信他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.97,0:16:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我有个提议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提议吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.92,0:16:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一个意想不到的提议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了 酷他们的状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人都似乎没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说休息一晚就会好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.68,0:16:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来一下行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想跟你们说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.73,0:16:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到守护翼居然要进攻煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.63,0:16:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想到了有可疑的家伙混入了上层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没想到居然到这地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.01,0:17:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依照沙威鲁德前辈的提议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,返回守护翼总部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将传说中所记载的力量一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向法鲁克总监和克鲁斯辅佐官汇报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽力说服议会中止进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.40,0:17:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以蕾和酷就拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.77,0:17:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让任何人妨碍他们两人决定做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.91,0:17:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总监他们也许能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议会那些家伙会改变已定了的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.44,0:17:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算议会不改变决议也必须阻止这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其意思是保护煌珠的双翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.27,0:17:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我相信那也是\N意味着煌珠和人类携手飞向未来的双翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.25,0:18:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以去吗 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.00,0:18:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.53,0:18:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.41,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是因为他们说\N要让蕾做其该做的事就必须杀了我什么的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.57,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是ChaosChoir那些家伙信口开河的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 是同一体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.96,0:19:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煌珠乐园和ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话更要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.16,0:19:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样逃来逃去不也无济于事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.09,0:19:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不希望再像菲萝那时侯一样伤心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.53,0:19:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们闯进煌珠乐园 干掉ChaosChoir吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛伊娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.12,0:19:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我出发前往守护翼总部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈你们也一定要保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.36,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹射器准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.65,0:21:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.89,0:21:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.30,0:22:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分别突然来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.92,0:22:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟那是否是再会的序曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.23,0:23:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二十三唱 约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.91,0:22:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.75,0:23:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年坚信少女那笑颜
